{"tid":1049512,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"YG梁鉉錫也出事！勝利另一間夜店爆逃稅","createTime":"2019-03-06T10:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T10:48:19.000Z","uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"166b8c44dfd820df4bce0043d4025ed655541523","tid":1049512,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"南韓藝人勝利風波越演越烈，事件爆發至今餘1個月，他的合夥人又被爆曾向警方行賄，警方也已掌握當初媒體報導他涉嫌性招待的部分對話內容，6日又有新進度，勝利另一間參與經營的夜店「lovesignal」有逃稅的嫌疑，且該店面實際所有主是YG社長梁鉉錫，醜聞一波未平一波又起。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3927/d3927621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3927%2Fd3927621.jpg&h=dd5ab1bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲勝利案件還在調查，事非卻越爆越多。（圖／達志影像）<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報導，勝利另一間參與經營的夜店「lovesignal」（前身為Club X）位於鬧區弘大，他曾在Instagram親自替夜店宣傳開幕，6日卻被挖出涉嫌逃稅，且該夜店並不是登記為娛樂場所經營，而是以一般餐廳的名義註冊，疑似為了逃稅才如此登記。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3938/d3938880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3938%2Fd3938880.jpg&h=bb9a3695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲勝利曾在IG宣傳自己在弘大經營的夜店，如今店家涉嫌逃稅。（圖／翻攝自IG）''<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3938/d3938881.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3938%2Fd3938881.jpg&h=7730360b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲但該間夜店所有人被爆是梁賢碩。（圖／翻攝自CFP）<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，韓媒進一步爆料，「lovesignal」店面登記的所有人其實是YG社長梁鉉錫，對此，YG以往都是沈默以對任何爆料，這次也不例外，面對報導內容暫無回應。"},{"pid":"0dfefe3390324ea4693d4a4e2f53d65e44978514","tid":1049512,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5fff82d79a0d361127c5baaa65d9af1e9cc53b","tid":1049512,"uid":74012,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"勝利我淨係記得佢扑女歌迷"},{"pid":"0182aebcd092f2742cc3288e8fb210e26095cc4d","tid":1049512,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b03f0f4644bb05b34eabc92962a6c6caec4c95f","tid":1049512,"uid":69769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:32:24.000Z","msg":"YG收得皮未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad769f74ffaceaf3401994f820c3f7bc6aca57d","tid":1049512,"uid":193951,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:37:24.000Z","msg":"其實YG係咪大型犯罪集團黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22c8ca6fabf52cb076d365c56217d5de545d081","tid":1049512,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6ad769f74ffaceaf3401994f820c3f7bc6aca57d","tid":1049512,"uid":193951,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:37:24.000Z","msg":"其實YG係咪大型犯罪集團黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"身為一個娛樂公司真係好犀利<br />\n簡直無惡不作"},{"pid":"98d6c2323b57ec9005803e0ff75cba4e5e263870","tid":1049512,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"好波 YG收皮"},{"pid":"e7fd8c6eb0c44245fb1c5caa901d8aecbbabcd15","tid":1049512,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:46:51.000Z","msg":"訓"},{"pid":"e736c80875a016e25a8363529cdcea93b39d0faa","tid":1049512,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ad769f74ffaceaf3401994f820c3f7bc6aca57d","tid":1049512,"uid":193951,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:37:24.000Z","msg":"其實YG係咪大型犯罪集團黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"除左BB仲有邊D?"}]}